reviews.review:
If you want to play this game you must accept some facts:
1 - Behaviour Interactive don't give a fuck about people breaking rules and life threatening you, they just want your money;
2 - Behaviour Interactive support don't give a fuck about your tickets, I have made one month ago and they still not answered;
2 - Players are toxic and they know they won't be punished for whatever they say(insult you or your family/racism/life threats);
3 - Devs will buff or nerf balanced killers for more profit;
4 - You would need to play hundred of matches to get enough buy your first killer/survivor;
5 - For some reason this game is full of streamers of all kinds;

TL;DR;
If you don't mind toxic players insulting you, devs breaking the game and Behaviour Interactive giving 0 fucks to it, this is a good game.
